1
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:26,030
[The Princess Royal]

2
00:01:26,030 --> 00:01:28,950
[Adapted from Mo Shu Bai's novel,
The Princess Royal on jjwxc.net]

3
00:01:28,950 --> 00:01:30,020
[This is a work of fiction.]

4
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
[Episode 15]

5
00:01:34,300 --> 00:01:35,100
Xun Chuan.

6
00:01:36,780 --> 00:01:37,580
Cut off his arm.

7
00:01:39,020 --> 00:01:39,660
Yes.

8
00:01:41,900 --> 00:01:43,300
No. Please don't!

9
00:01:43,300 --> 00:01:43,980
Slowly.

10
00:01:47,300 --> 00:01:51,660
♪If the past was caught
in the turbulent waves of the storm♪

11
00:01:51,660 --> 00:01:54,980
Actually, having you
hold my arm like this is really nice.

12
00:01:54,980 --> 00:01:57,860
♪Will there be arms to hold me
in this lifetime?♪

13
00:01:57,860 --> 00:01:59,060
Are you stupid?

14
00:01:59,820 --> 00:02:00,740
Why are you still joking around?

15
00:02:01,740 --> 00:02:03,180
Don't you know what they are up to?

16
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:04,820
Don't worry.

17
00:02:05,220 --> 00:02:05,700
Slowly.

18
00:02:05,700 --> 00:02:07,060
Everything is as I anticipated.

19
00:02:08,220 --> 00:02:09,260
What did you anticipate?

20
00:02:09,980 --> 00:02:10,980
Did it ever occur to you

21
00:02:11,220 --> 00:02:12,940
that if your second uncle had aimed
to seriously harm you today

22
00:02:13,260 --> 00:02:14,540
and have someone cripple you

23
00:02:14,540 --> 00:02:15,500
before I could get there,

24
00:02:15,620 --> 00:02:16,900
wouldn't your life be ruined?

25
00:02:16,900 --> 00:02:18,340
♪Guides me through the worldly remnants
of old dreams♪

26
00:02:18,340 --> 00:02:19,380
Don't be mad.

27
00:02:20,060 --> 00:02:21,540
I already told you,

28
00:02:21,740 --> 00:02:23,820
this was all part of my plan.

29
00:02:23,820 --> 00:02:26,880
♪Hidden in my sleeves♪

30
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:29,780
Why didn't you go eat with Su Rongqing?

31
00:02:30,900 --> 00:02:32,380
I instructed them

32
00:02:32,420 --> 00:02:33,620
not to bother you.

33
00:02:34,980 --> 00:02:36,580
♪Lighting up the misty sea tower♪

34
00:02:36,580 --> 00:02:37,980
♪Allowing you and me to dock safely♪

35
00:02:37,980 --> 00:02:39,020
What's wrong with you...

36
00:02:40,220 --> 00:02:40,980
Be gentle, please.

37
00:02:40,980 --> 00:02:41,860
It hurts.

38
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:43,300
♪In this long and arduous journey♪

39
00:02:43,300 --> 00:02:44,140
Pei Wenxuan,

40
00:02:45,460 --> 00:02:47,460
why do you always
put yourself on the line?

41
00:02:48,180 --> 00:02:49,380
When will you realize

42
00:02:49,380 --> 00:02:50,140
how important you are

43
00:02:50,140 --> 00:02:50,940
and start taking care of yourself?

44
00:02:50,940 --> 00:02:53,060
I'm hurting so much,
so please stop talking.

45
00:02:53,220 --> 00:02:54,020
Just let me lean on you.

46
00:02:54,020 --> 00:02:55,240
♪That makes me willing
to set aside my pride♪

47
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:58,600
♪Even if the world falls into my grasp♪

48
00:02:58,740 --> 00:03:01,660
♪Your eyes would still captivate me♪

49
00:03:01,660 --> 00:03:02,460
Don't worry.

50
00:03:02,460 --> 00:03:05,180
♪I'll stay by your side
till the end of time♪

51
00:03:05,180 --> 00:03:07,180
I will definitely become stronger.

52
00:03:09,060 --> 00:03:10,620
♪In this long and arduous journey♪

53
00:03:10,620 --> 00:03:11,580
I will.

54
00:03:12,100 --> 00:03:15,860
♪I'm fortunate to have met you♪

55
00:03:15,860 --> 00:03:18,420
♪It is your tenderness♪

56
00:03:18,660 --> 00:03:19,780
It's not I cannot bear
to see you suffer.

57
00:03:19,780 --> 00:03:22,220
♪That makes me willing
to set aside my pride♪

58
00:03:22,700 --> 00:03:25,180
I'm just annoyed
that you've embarrassed me.

59
00:03:25,580 --> 00:03:28,980
♪Your eyes would still captivate me♪

60
00:03:29,340 --> 00:03:30,780
♪I'll stay by your side
till the end of time♪

61
00:03:30,780 --> 00:03:31,660
Listen up,

62
00:03:32,380 --> 00:03:33,580
you're my husband,

63
00:03:34,220 --> 00:03:35,540
so only I can bully you.

64
00:03:37,020 --> 00:03:37,620
Understand?

65
00:03:37,620 --> 00:03:39,260
♪May we stay together in dreams♪

66
00:03:40,100 --> 00:03:40,740
Understood.

67
00:03:40,740 --> 00:03:43,500
♪With the starry sky as our bed
and our embraces as our quilt♪

68
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:45,980
♪Regardless of the seasons♪

69
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:49,020
♪We will journey through life together
until the very end♪

70
00:03:49,020 --> 00:03:50,140
Young Master.

71
00:03:50,740 --> 00:03:51,460
Young Master,

72
00:03:51,740 --> 00:03:53,700
would you two like to continue
somewhere else?

73
00:03:54,260 --> 00:03:55,180
Here. Hold him steadily.

74
00:03:56,220 --> 00:03:56,860
Slowly.

75
00:03:56,860 --> 00:03:59,820
♪For with you, each moment is timeless♪

76
00:03:59,820 --> 00:04:00,420
Let's go.

77
00:04:00,700 --> 00:04:01,380
Let's go.

78
00:04:04,260 --> 00:04:04,900
Come on.

79
00:04:20,620 --> 00:04:23,300
Is Her Highness not coming?

80
00:04:26,780 --> 00:04:29,020
Having a big meal here
just by the two of us

81
00:04:29,140 --> 00:04:30,060
seems quite nice too.

82
00:04:30,540 --> 00:04:31,340
Don't you think so?

83
00:04:34,580 --> 00:04:35,340
Of course.

84
00:04:36,020 --> 00:04:36,740
Cheers, Ronghua.

85
00:04:37,100 --> 00:04:37,740
Cheers.

86
00:04:43,620 --> 00:04:44,860
Her Highness's absence

87
00:04:45,780 --> 00:04:47,660
can only be due to Pei Wenxuan, I guess.

88
00:04:53,060 --> 00:04:54,300
Let the Imperial Physician handle it.

89
00:04:54,460 --> 00:04:55,620
It's not helpful if you do it.

90
00:05:00,900 --> 00:05:02,300
Can't you feel any pain?

91
00:05:04,540 --> 00:05:05,260
Yeah.

92
00:05:05,500 --> 00:05:06,500
I'm already used to it.

93
00:05:09,860 --> 00:05:12,340
But it's my fault for letting you

94
00:05:12,340 --> 00:05:13,420
suffer along with me.

95
00:05:13,620 --> 00:05:14,980
It's good though that I'm injured.

96
00:05:15,180 --> 00:05:16,540
My mother is easily swayed.

97
00:05:16,860 --> 00:05:19,180
If we can persuade her to take our side,

98
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:21,820
we can take her
to negotiate with my grandfather

99
00:05:22,620 --> 00:05:24,220
and reclaim the inheritance

100
00:05:24,940 --> 00:05:26,060
from my father.

101
00:05:26,300 --> 00:05:27,100
Be gentle, please.

102
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:33,900
Pei Wenxuan,

103
00:05:34,540 --> 00:05:36,060
you shouldn't push yourself
so hard in the future.

104
00:05:36,380 --> 00:05:37,620
Seeing you like this...

105
00:05:39,020 --> 00:05:40,180
makes me feel bad.

106
00:05:42,780 --> 00:05:44,460
Next time you encounter
something like this,

107
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:46,940
at least let me know in advance.

108
00:05:46,940 --> 00:05:48,500
Whether or not you have a plan,

109
00:05:48,900 --> 00:05:50,180
it will give me some peace of mind.

110
00:05:50,460 --> 00:05:52,260
You said I didn't consider
others' difficulties,

111
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:53,700
but you, on the other hand,

112
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:56,300
care too much
about others' difficulties.

113
00:06:01,020 --> 00:06:03,900
I'll take it as a compliment,
Your Highness.

114
00:06:09,340 --> 00:06:10,580
I'm going to apply
the ointment for you now.

115
00:06:14,780 --> 00:06:16,140
I used to hear you say

116
00:06:17,060 --> 00:06:18,580
that you didn't want
to be like your father

117
00:06:19,220 --> 00:06:20,730
and that he spoiled your mother too much

118
00:06:20,730 --> 00:06:22,100
so she didn't understand anything.

119
00:06:22,100 --> 00:06:23,460
If she can't learn to protect you,

120
00:06:23,460 --> 00:06:24,460
why did she give birth to you?

121
00:06:24,460 --> 00:06:25,820
Does she even deserve to be a mother,

122
00:06:26,300 --> 00:06:28,060
leaving you to suffer out there
on your own?

123
00:06:32,500 --> 00:06:33,780
Alright, I won't say any more.

124
00:06:34,780 --> 00:06:35,860
Watching you act like this

125
00:06:36,300 --> 00:06:37,500
is frustrating.

126
00:06:39,140 --> 00:06:39,940
Yes.

127
00:06:40,260 --> 00:06:42,220
It's me who made you frustrated.

128
00:06:46,420 --> 00:06:48,540
Ms. Wen is your mother.

129
00:06:49,740 --> 00:06:51,580
Whether she is weak or incompetent,

130
00:06:51,700 --> 00:06:53,020
she must fight for you at least once.

131
00:06:54,660 --> 00:06:56,260
You can't always think of others

132
00:06:56,420 --> 00:06:57,580
and make yourself suffer.

133
00:06:58,620 --> 00:07:01,260
If you want something,
you have to fight for it yourself.

134
00:07:01,620 --> 00:07:02,460
Do you understand?

135
00:07:06,460 --> 00:07:10,300
What if she's unwilling?

136
00:07:10,580 --> 00:07:12,100
Then she can refuse.

137
00:07:13,700 --> 00:07:14,940
Whether she wants it or not,

138
00:07:15,300 --> 00:07:17,380
you have to give her a choice, right?

139
00:07:20,020 --> 00:07:21,220
But I already know

140
00:07:21,780 --> 00:07:23,340
which path is better for her.

141
00:07:26,340 --> 00:07:27,180
Pei Wenxuan,

142
00:07:28,340 --> 00:07:30,460
only the person involved

143
00:07:30,940 --> 00:07:32,140
knows which path is better.

144
00:07:39,940 --> 00:07:40,900
I will carefully consider

145
00:07:41,500 --> 00:07:42,820
your words.

146
00:07:44,340 --> 00:07:47,020
If you can figure it out,
that would be best.

147
00:07:47,940 --> 00:07:48,660
After all,

148
00:07:49,660 --> 00:07:51,100
I can't protect you forever.

149
00:08:00,140 --> 00:08:01,700
I'm fine, Ronghua.

150
00:08:03,820 --> 00:08:04,420
Rongqing,

151
00:08:05,220 --> 00:08:07,660
It seems I should take you out
for drinks more often.

152
00:08:10,420 --> 00:08:11,180
You have been suppressing your emotions

153
00:08:11,580 --> 00:08:13,220
and behaving yourself at home
for too long.

154
00:08:17,620 --> 00:08:19,780
If it's what I experienced today,

155
00:08:20,340 --> 00:08:21,060
then one time

156
00:08:21,940 --> 00:08:22,700
is more than enough.

157
00:08:54,900 --> 00:08:56,060
Why are you looking at me?

158
00:08:58,180 --> 00:08:59,260
You are pretty.

159
00:09:01,540 --> 00:09:03,020
Smooth talker.

160
00:09:07,660 --> 00:09:08,340
Your Highness,

161
00:09:09,140 --> 00:09:11,660
what kind of a person do you think I am?

162
00:09:16,220 --> 00:09:18,980
What do you mean by that?

163
00:09:24,020 --> 00:09:24,700
Never mind.

164
00:09:25,340 --> 00:09:26,740
I guess you are tired.

165
00:09:28,380 --> 00:09:29,980
You just want me to praise you, right?

166
00:09:30,940 --> 00:09:31,740
No.

167
00:09:33,700 --> 00:09:34,820
You learn everything so quickly.

168
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:38,540
I remember the first time
you did my eyebrows,

169
00:09:39,700 --> 00:09:41,380
it was all crooked.

170
00:09:41,940 --> 00:09:43,180
But within a month,

171
00:09:43,580 --> 00:09:44,940
you even knew how to do makeup.

172
00:09:45,980 --> 00:09:47,700
The first time you did my hair,

173
00:09:47,820 --> 00:09:49,020
you pulled so hard which was so painful,

174
00:09:49,540 --> 00:09:50,460
but after that,

175
00:09:51,060 --> 00:09:52,700
there wasn't a hairstyle
you couldn't do.

176
00:09:54,380 --> 00:09:55,780
If I'm good to you in any way,

177
00:09:56,300 --> 00:09:58,620
you respond
with ten times the gratitude and joy.

178
00:10:03,020 --> 00:10:03,820
To be honest...

179
00:10:06,300 --> 00:10:09,820
whether as a husband, a friend,

180
00:10:10,900 --> 00:10:12,060
or a family member...

181
00:10:14,020 --> 00:10:15,380
if everyone were like me,

182
00:10:16,820 --> 00:10:18,140
nonchalant about everything,

183
00:10:18,180 --> 00:10:19,500
and letting everything go easily...

184
00:10:21,420 --> 00:10:23,020
life would be a bit boring.

185
00:10:25,380 --> 00:10:26,420
Anyway,

186
00:10:27,180 --> 00:10:28,540
you're truly wonderful.

187
00:10:28,540 --> 00:10:30,180
You just don't realize it yourself.

188
00:10:31,900 --> 00:10:32,780
Now, I know.

189
00:10:40,700 --> 00:10:41,420
What is it?

190
00:10:41,700 --> 00:10:42,420
My back hurts.

191
00:10:43,060 --> 00:10:43,900
What should we do then?

192
00:10:49,180 --> 00:10:49,940
What are you doing?

193
00:10:51,540 --> 00:10:52,660
Your back hurts...

194
00:10:53,420 --> 00:10:54,700
It hurts. Don't move.

195
00:10:56,060 --> 00:10:57,580
I don't want to let go anymore.

196
00:10:57,580 --> 00:10:59,420
♪May time itself ask me♪

197
00:10:59,420 --> 00:11:02,180
♪How many glances does it take
in a lifetime♪

198
00:11:02,300 --> 00:11:04,180
What do you mean
by you don't want to let go anymore?

199
00:11:04,180 --> 00:11:06,900
♪To be blessed
with your highs and your lows?♪

200
00:11:08,020 --> 00:11:09,780
♪I've cherished every second of my life♪

201
00:11:09,780 --> 00:11:13,820
♪Embracing your joys and sorrows♪

202
00:11:13,820 --> 00:11:15,260
♪Serenely♪

203
00:11:15,260 --> 00:11:17,420
♪Allowing the flower of love to bloom♪

204
00:11:17,420 --> 00:11:20,500
You want to keep holding me like this?

205
00:11:20,500 --> 00:11:22,820
♪I thought capturing your heart
meant forever♪

206
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:24,860
♪Yet, it turned out to be
as fleeting as autumn♪

207
00:11:24,860 --> 00:11:27,020
♪Without you♪

208
00:11:27,140 --> 00:11:30,340
♪Even the hustle and bustle
can still feel lonely♪

209
00:11:31,380 --> 00:11:33,540
♪Even if past moments
vanish without a trace♪

210
00:11:33,540 --> 00:11:34,300
It's alright.

211
00:11:34,900 --> 00:11:35,660
I know

212
00:11:36,380 --> 00:11:38,140
you must feel horrible today.

213
00:11:38,780 --> 00:11:40,060
Keep holding me if you want to.

214
00:11:40,180 --> 00:11:41,500
It's okay. Well,

215
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:42,540
I'll sleep now.

216
00:11:43,140 --> 00:11:44,430
Your family will definitely complain
about me tomorrow

217
00:11:44,430 --> 00:11:45,300
during the morning court.

218
00:11:45,300 --> 00:11:48,540
♪Let me face trials and tribulations
with you♪

219
00:11:48,540 --> 00:11:54,700
♪Let us bathe in love's endless grace♪

220
00:11:54,700 --> 00:12:00,260
♪Even if past moments
vanish without a trace♪

221
00:12:00,500 --> 00:12:06,260
♪Grant me a ceaseless passion♪

222
00:12:06,340 --> 00:12:09,180
♪Let me face trials and tribulations
with you♪

223
00:12:09,180 --> 00:12:09,780
Your Majesty,

224
00:12:10,300 --> 00:12:11,700
here are the memorials
for you to go through.

225
00:12:12,540 --> 00:12:15,180
The ones on top are from the Pei Family

226
00:12:16,180 --> 00:12:17,020
who accuses

227
00:12:17,780 --> 00:12:19,300
Her Highness of being overbearing

228
00:12:19,420 --> 00:12:20,780
and the Inspectorate Office
of being unjust.

229
00:12:21,380 --> 00:12:24,020
Down below are the memorials
from the noble families

230
00:12:24,940 --> 00:12:25,820
stating

231
00:12:26,580 --> 00:12:29,060
that Her Highness
did not respect her parents-in-law.

232
00:12:29,820 --> 00:12:30,700
They have also

233
00:12:36,620 --> 00:12:38,890
[The Classic of Filial Piety]
sent a carved copy

234
00:12:38,890 --> 00:12:41,500
of the Classic of Filial Piety,

235
00:12:42,300 --> 00:12:44,540
asking you to hand it over
to Her Highness.

236
00:12:47,660 --> 00:12:49,300
They are kind of thoughtful.

237
00:12:50,060 --> 00:12:51,780
Pingyue went to the Pei Family,

238
00:12:52,820 --> 00:12:54,700
and now the entire Huajing
knows about it.

239
00:13:04,620 --> 00:13:05,500
Your Highness.

240
00:13:08,580 --> 00:13:09,260
Mr. Su.

241
00:13:13,820 --> 00:13:14,500
Yesterday...

242
00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:17,860
Yesterday, my brother and I left
right after we finished eating.

243
00:13:18,220 --> 00:13:19,300
It was no big deal.

244
00:13:19,780 --> 00:13:21,740
Don't worry.

245
00:13:24,020 --> 00:13:26,020
Yesterday, I indeed
had an urgent matter come up.

246
00:13:26,700 --> 00:13:28,300
I will treat you some other time.

247
00:13:30,260 --> 00:13:31,060
Your Highness,

248
00:13:31,860 --> 00:13:32,700
there's no need for that actually.

249
00:13:33,620 --> 00:13:35,500
Given your sensitive status now,

250
00:13:35,860 --> 00:13:37,940
it's best we limit our interactions

251
00:13:38,300 --> 00:13:41,140
to avoid stirring up gossip
among the ministers.

252
00:13:43,740 --> 00:13:45,380
When I agreed with my brother yesterday,

253
00:13:45,940 --> 00:13:47,420
I didn't know you would also come.

254
00:13:48,020 --> 00:13:48,780
So,

255
00:13:49,540 --> 00:13:52,060
if I had known,
I wouldn't have agreed.

256
00:13:56,860 --> 00:13:57,820
That's good then.

257
00:14:03,300 --> 00:14:04,340
I won't keep you any longer.

258
00:14:04,500 --> 00:14:05,420
I'll take my leave.

259
00:14:07,660 --> 00:14:08,540
Take care, Your Highness.

260
00:14:13,820 --> 00:14:14,620
Your Highness,

261
00:14:15,460 --> 00:14:17,460
I didn't mean what I said just now.

262
00:14:18,300 --> 00:14:19,100
Everyone,

263
00:14:19,860 --> 00:14:22,140
do you have any important matters
to report today?

264
00:14:24,380 --> 00:14:25,180
Father,

265
00:14:26,180 --> 00:14:27,740
you must seek justice for me.

266
00:14:28,660 --> 00:14:30,380
What justice do you want me
to seek for you?

267
00:14:30,940 --> 00:14:31,780
Tell me about it.

268
00:14:31,900 --> 00:14:32,660
Yesterday,

269
00:14:33,340 --> 00:14:35,980
Mr. Pei sent for my husband
to return to Pei's Mansion,

270
00:14:36,300 --> 00:14:37,500
claiming that my mother-in-law
was seriously sick.

271
00:14:38,100 --> 00:14:39,780
My husband rushed back in worry,

272
00:14:40,180 --> 00:14:41,420
but as soon as he got there,

273
00:14:41,540 --> 00:14:43,380
Mr. Pei's men beat him up.

274
00:14:45,620 --> 00:14:46,300
Your Majesty,

275
00:14:46,860 --> 00:14:49,580
what Her Highness said
is far from the truth.

276
00:14:49,820 --> 00:14:52,060
Since the Prince Consort
married Her Highness,

277
00:14:52,140 --> 00:14:54,180
he has never returned home
to visit his mother.

278
00:14:54,340 --> 00:14:56,220
Lately, my sister-in-law has been unwell

279
00:14:56,380 --> 00:14:57,860
and asked the Prince Consort
to come back many times,

280
00:14:57,860 --> 00:14:59,500
but he ignored her every time.

281
00:14:59,540 --> 00:15:02,540
Initially, we hoped to persuade Wenxuan

282
00:15:02,540 --> 00:15:04,660
to return to the right path

283
00:15:04,660 --> 00:15:05,900
and carry out his filial duties
to his mother.

284
00:15:05,900 --> 00:15:08,700
But Wenxuan not only refused to listen

285
00:15:08,700 --> 00:15:10,100
but also injured some servants.

286
00:15:10,220 --> 00:15:13,100
He even threatened
that he had Her Highness's support

287
00:15:13,180 --> 00:15:14,580
and no one could touch him.

288
00:15:14,820 --> 00:15:18,180
Later, Her Highness led troops
to barge into our Mansion

289
00:15:18,300 --> 00:15:19,660
and took the Prince Consort away.

290
00:15:19,660 --> 00:15:22,980
Before leaving, she even broke
the arms of two servants.

291
00:15:23,500 --> 00:15:26,380
Her Highness
is so overbearing and arrogant.

292
00:15:26,380 --> 00:15:27,780
She disregards all propriety.

293
00:15:28,060 --> 00:15:30,380
Yet now she's here, falsely accusing us

294
00:15:30,380 --> 00:15:31,660
and sullying our Pei Family's name...

295
00:15:31,860 --> 00:15:32,620
Insolence.

296
00:15:33,260 --> 00:15:35,500
From what I can tell,
it was you who started it first.

297
00:15:35,700 --> 00:15:36,860
May I ask, Mr. Pei,

298
00:15:37,300 --> 00:15:38,700
according to the etiquettes
of our dynasty,

299
00:15:38,700 --> 00:15:40,820
you should get the imperial family's
and Princess Pingyue's permission

300
00:15:41,220 --> 00:15:42,700
before punishing the Prince Consort.
But did you do that?

301
00:15:42,860 --> 00:15:43,580
Enough!

302
00:15:44,300 --> 00:15:46,380
This is all just your family's affair,

303
00:15:46,500 --> 00:15:48,460
yet you bring it
to the court and argue here.

304
00:15:48,740 --> 00:15:51,060
What about the imperial family's
reputation?

305
00:15:51,380 --> 00:15:52,580
You hit the Prince Consort

306
00:15:52,660 --> 00:15:53,940
and then Pingyue saved him.

307
00:15:54,580 --> 00:15:56,060
What more is there to argue about?

308
00:15:57,180 --> 00:15:57,980
Your Majesty,

309
00:16:00,060 --> 00:16:01,980
Her Highness has just established
the Inspectorate Office...

310
00:16:02,860 --> 00:16:04,020
Are you done yet?

311
00:16:04,460 --> 00:16:05,260
Regardless,

312
00:16:05,260 --> 00:16:06,860
Pei Wenxuan is my son-in-law

313
00:16:06,860 --> 00:16:08,060
and part of the imperial family.

314
00:16:08,820 --> 00:16:09,940
Do not mention this again.

315
00:16:12,740 --> 00:16:14,980
I have heard
that three administrative divisions

316
00:16:15,180 --> 00:16:16,260
have been dry for a long time,
possibly leading to a severe drought.

317
00:16:16,900 --> 00:16:19,380
Everyone, quickly devise a solution.

318
00:16:22,860 --> 00:16:23,660
Rou,

319
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:26,140
is it really appropriate for us

320
00:16:26,820 --> 00:16:27,940
to head out like this?

321
00:16:28,140 --> 00:16:28,900
Madam,

322
00:16:29,020 --> 00:16:31,180
First Young Master is in need \
of your support right now.

323
00:16:31,700 --> 00:16:32,660
Please think it over.

324
00:16:33,220 --> 00:16:34,020
Okay.

325
00:16:34,700 --> 00:16:35,300
Let's go.

326
00:16:35,460 --> 00:16:36,220
Your Highness.

327
00:16:40,060 --> 00:16:42,260
Do you have no qualms

328
00:16:42,820 --> 00:16:44,660
about lying so blatantly today?

329
00:16:49,380 --> 00:16:50,780
That's the question I want to ask you.

330
00:16:51,780 --> 00:16:53,420
Whether it's a lie or not,

331
00:16:53,500 --> 00:16:55,660
a mother teaching her son
is a matter of course.

332
00:16:55,820 --> 00:16:57,700
But it's inappropriate for you

333
00:16:57,780 --> 00:16:59,060
to break into a minister's mansion.

334
00:16:59,340 --> 00:17:01,220
Why didn't you say this
to my father earlier?

335
00:17:01,860 --> 00:17:03,780
You didn't dare utter a word
in the hall just now

336
00:17:03,780 --> 00:17:04,900
and now you're here to criticize me.

337
00:17:05,460 --> 00:17:06,420
If you're so justified,

338
00:17:06,540 --> 00:17:07,420
go ahead and tell my father.

339
00:17:07,940 --> 00:17:08,740
Your Highness,

340
00:17:08,940 --> 00:17:10,300
you're being too overbearing.

341
00:17:10,380 --> 00:17:11,380
Go and complain about me then.

342
00:17:12,700 --> 00:17:13,940
If you really can't stand it...

343
00:17:15,260 --> 00:17:16,460
then hit me too.

344
00:17:16,500 --> 00:17:17,620
Your Highness, you are...

345
00:17:26,980 --> 00:17:29,220
I really like your how you look

346
00:17:29,460 --> 00:17:32,180
when you all can't stand me
but can't do anything about it.

347
00:17:34,020 --> 00:17:36,740
I won't dwell on this matter today

348
00:17:37,580 --> 00:17:38,820
but mark my words...

349
00:17:40,020 --> 00:17:41,500
you'll apologize to me someday.

350
00:17:42,380 --> 00:17:43,740
You may all leave now.

351
00:17:44,380 --> 00:17:45,620
I have a case to handle.

352
00:17:47,420 --> 00:17:48,300
Your Highness.

353
00:17:50,580 --> 00:17:53,740
The court of Great Xia
won't allow you to act so insolently

354
00:17:53,740 --> 00:17:55,220
without facing the consequences.

355
00:17:55,220 --> 00:17:57,500
I will go to the Imperial Study
to see His Majesty now.

356
00:17:57,500 --> 00:17:59,340
If you are not severely punished today,

357
00:17:59,580 --> 00:18:01,620
I will throw myself to death
at the Shoulong Pillar

358
00:18:01,620 --> 00:18:02,700
to protest.

359
00:18:03,940 --> 00:18:04,660
I'm going too.

360
00:18:04,740 --> 00:18:05,340
Me too.

361
00:18:05,700 --> 00:18:06,580
We all will go.

362
00:18:08,220 --> 00:18:09,060
Great,

363
00:18:10,060 --> 00:18:11,700
I was planning to let it slide,

364
00:18:11,860 --> 00:18:13,740
but you've all insisted
on challenging me.

365
00:18:14,900 --> 00:18:16,020
The Imperial Study?

366
00:18:16,220 --> 00:18:16,940
Fine.

367
00:18:17,500 --> 00:18:19,340
Today, it's either you

368
00:18:19,620 --> 00:18:20,980
or me being carried out.

369
00:18:22,380 --> 00:18:23,020
Let's go.

370
00:18:25,740 --> 00:18:26,460
Let's go.

371
00:18:38,100 --> 00:18:41,260
Princess Pingle unlawfully barged
into Pei's Mansion without cause.

372
00:18:41,580 --> 00:18:43,260
Your Majesty, I urge you
to punish her severely.

373
00:18:43,580 --> 00:18:44,820
A princess who disregards the law

374
00:18:44,820 --> 00:18:46,460
and acts overbearingly and recklessly

375
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:49,140
must not hold a key position
in the Inspection Department.

376
00:18:49,580 --> 00:18:50,740
Father, I implore you to severely punish

377
00:18:50,740 --> 00:18:52,700
Pei Lixian and Pei Liming.

378
00:18:53,260 --> 00:18:54,500
They deceived their sister-in-law,

379
00:18:54,700 --> 00:18:56,180
mistreated their late brother's son,

380
00:18:56,180 --> 00:18:57,740
seized
their deceased brother's property,

381
00:18:57,900 --> 00:18:59,380
and assaulted the Prince Consort,
thereby offending the sovereign.

382
00:19:00,100 --> 00:19:01,660
Such shameless,

383
00:19:01,820 --> 00:19:03,340
ruthless, and cunning individuals

384
00:19:03,500 --> 00:19:04,620
must not be tolerated.

385
00:19:04,940 --> 00:19:05,740
Your Majesty.

386
00:19:05,900 --> 00:19:06,700
Father.

387
00:19:06,700 --> 00:19:08,140
Your Majesty, please see the truth.

388
00:19:08,300 --> 00:19:09,540
Father, please see the truth.

389
00:19:14,930 --> 00:19:17,740
[Hanqiu Palace]

390
00:19:17,740 --> 00:19:18,500
Your Highness,

391
00:19:19,140 --> 00:19:20,060
sirs,

392
00:19:20,220 --> 00:19:21,180
His Majesty has said

393
00:19:21,340 --> 00:19:22,620
that this is a family matter of yours.

394
00:19:23,060 --> 00:19:24,100
So please, everyone,
return to your duties.

395
00:19:25,140 --> 00:19:27,300
How can it be a family matter
when Her Highness

396
00:19:27,300 --> 00:19:29,020
is the head of the Inspectorate Office?

397
00:19:29,300 --> 00:19:31,580
If Your Majesty
doesn't seek justice for me today,

398
00:19:31,580 --> 00:19:32,820
I will kneel here

399
00:19:32,820 --> 00:19:34,180
until I die.

400
00:19:34,380 --> 00:19:36,100
Didn't you say you would end your life?

401
00:19:37,100 --> 00:19:39,580
Mr. Pei, you should stick to your word.

402
00:19:41,220 --> 00:19:43,780
I'm not going to argue
with a woman like you.

403
00:19:43,900 --> 00:19:45,500
You can't even win an argument
with a woman.

404
00:19:45,780 --> 00:19:47,340
It seems you have no reason
on your side.

405
00:19:47,660 --> 00:19:50,340
You might as well run headlong
into a pillar and save your reputation.

406
00:19:52,580 --> 00:19:54,100
Eunuch Fu, please inform His Majesty

407
00:19:54,300 --> 00:19:56,620
that if he does not severely punish
the princess,

408
00:19:56,780 --> 00:19:58,780
we will not leave here today.

409
00:19:58,820 --> 00:20:00,420
Eunuch Fu, please also tell Father

410
00:20:00,780 --> 00:20:03,380
that if he does not seek justice
for my husband today,

411
00:20:03,820 --> 00:20:04,780
I won't leave either.

412
00:20:06,020 --> 00:20:06,740
Your Highness,

413
00:20:07,220 --> 00:20:08,900
please stop making a scene.

414
00:20:09,020 --> 00:20:09,980
They are the ones making a scene.

415
00:20:10,860 --> 00:20:12,140
Please just convey
what I said to Father.

416
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:17,860
[Princess's Mansion]

417
00:20:20,700 --> 00:20:21,380
Wenxuan.

418
00:20:21,380 --> 00:20:22,020
Mother.

419
00:20:22,020 --> 00:20:23,100
How are you?

420
00:20:23,460 --> 00:20:24,300
I'm fine.

421
00:20:25,020 --> 00:20:25,700
Take a seat.

422
00:20:25,900 --> 00:20:26,700
Slowly.

423
00:20:26,780 --> 00:20:27,420
I'm alright.

424
00:20:38,060 --> 00:20:39,060
Wenxuan.

425
00:20:41,580 --> 00:20:42,700
About last night's incident,

426
00:20:43,740 --> 00:20:45,340
you must be blaming me,

427
00:20:45,780 --> 00:20:46,660
right?

428
00:20:48,780 --> 00:20:52,100
Do you think your second uncle
wants to harm you

429
00:20:52,500 --> 00:20:53,620
and treats you poorly?

430
00:20:54,060 --> 00:20:54,740
Mother,

431
00:20:56,220 --> 00:20:57,420
it's not what I think.

432
00:20:58,460 --> 00:21:00,180
It's just the way things are.

433
00:21:00,500 --> 00:21:03,580
Could there be
any misunderstanding here?

434
00:21:03,660 --> 00:21:05,460
Your second uncle told me...

435
00:21:05,700 --> 00:21:06,340
Mother,

436
00:21:08,020 --> 00:21:09,980
it's not so much what he said,

437
00:21:10,940 --> 00:21:12,420
but what he did.

438
00:21:14,300 --> 00:21:16,380
I've never dared to tell you this.

439
00:21:18,900 --> 00:21:20,740
When Father passed away years ago,

440
00:21:21,460 --> 00:21:23,140
I was ambushed

441
00:21:24,020 --> 00:21:25,900
on my way back from Luzhou.

442
00:21:26,660 --> 00:21:27,460
Ambushed?

443
00:21:28,300 --> 00:21:29,100
Yes.

444
00:21:30,020 --> 00:21:31,060
I later found out

445
00:21:32,060 --> 00:21:33,500
it was Second Uncle's doing.

446
00:21:33,500 --> 00:21:34,020
You...

447
00:21:35,620 --> 00:21:37,620
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

448
00:21:37,620 --> 00:21:38,700
Because it wouldn't have helped.

449
00:21:41,220 --> 00:21:44,140
I know you well.

450
00:21:45,420 --> 00:21:46,900
When I returned that year,

451
00:21:47,740 --> 00:21:49,500
there was no one by your side anymore.

452
00:21:51,700 --> 00:21:54,820
If you had known about it
and tried to do something,

453
00:21:55,860 --> 00:21:57,780
you would have been targeted by them.

454
00:21:58,420 --> 00:21:59,460
Instead of that,

455
00:21:59,500 --> 00:22:00,860
it's better

456
00:22:00,860 --> 00:22:01,940
for you to not know anything

457
00:22:02,140 --> 00:22:03,580
and live a peaceful life.

458
00:22:08,460 --> 00:22:10,540
When Father was still alive,

459
00:22:11,740 --> 00:22:13,380
he often reminded me

460
00:22:14,660 --> 00:22:15,460
that as men...

461
00:22:17,020 --> 00:22:18,460
we should shoulder

462
00:22:19,220 --> 00:22:20,740
responsibilities

463
00:22:20,940 --> 00:22:23,540
and strive to make those around us
live a better life.

464
00:22:26,140 --> 00:22:27,820
If they are not living a good life...

465
00:22:29,420 --> 00:22:31,060
we should be the ones to be blamed.

466
00:22:32,060 --> 00:22:33,300
And it's evident

467
00:22:34,540 --> 00:22:35,900
that Father fulfilled his duties.

468
00:22:36,660 --> 00:22:39,180
He spent his whole life
taking care of you.

469
00:22:40,100 --> 00:22:41,540
You didn't have to do

470
00:22:41,740 --> 00:22:43,140
or think about anything.

471
00:22:45,220 --> 00:22:46,700
Later, Father told me

472
00:22:47,260 --> 00:22:48,740
to take on his responsibilities

473
00:22:48,740 --> 00:22:49,940
and continue caring for you.

474
00:22:50,340 --> 00:22:51,580
And I've always seen this

475
00:22:52,020 --> 00:22:53,580
as my own battle.

476
00:22:55,620 --> 00:22:57,980
Whether I win or lose...

477
00:22:59,820 --> 00:23:01,300
I shouldn't disturb you.

478
00:23:06,700 --> 00:23:08,980
Then why bring it up now?

479
00:23:10,060 --> 00:23:11,580
Did I end up harming you...

480
00:23:13,540 --> 00:23:15,500
and leaving you no way out?

481
00:23:15,940 --> 00:23:16,900
That's not it.

482
00:23:17,820 --> 00:23:19,140
It's because someone

483
00:23:20,820 --> 00:23:21,940
told me...

484
00:23:24,540 --> 00:23:26,060
that I should allow you
to make your own choice.

485
00:23:28,660 --> 00:23:30,340
Father took all the responsibilities

486
00:23:30,620 --> 00:23:32,060
upon himself

487
00:23:33,260 --> 00:23:36,180
but never let you choose.

488
00:23:38,300 --> 00:23:39,140
So, Mother,

489
00:23:39,980 --> 00:23:40,860
this time...

490
00:23:42,700 --> 00:23:44,700
I want you to make your own choice.

491
00:23:48,420 --> 00:23:49,100
Young Master.

492
00:23:49,660 --> 00:23:50,340
Young Master.

493
00:23:51,780 --> 00:23:52,380
Madam.

494
00:23:52,740 --> 00:23:54,060
Young Master,

495
00:23:54,060 --> 00:23:55,580
Second Master led many ministers

496
00:23:55,580 --> 00:23:58,340
to kneel at the door
of the Imperial Study,
demanding punishment for Her Highness.

497
00:23:58,340 --> 00:23:59,660
She, in turn, knelt there too,

498
00:23:59,740 --> 00:24:01,460
insisting on punishment
for Second and Third Masters.

499
00:24:01,460 --> 00:24:02,380
They've been kneeling there,

500
00:24:02,380 --> 00:24:03,780
deadlocked, for quite a while now.

501
00:24:04,020 --> 00:24:04,940
Get the carriage ready.

502
00:24:05,300 --> 00:24:05,980
I'm going to the palace.

503
00:24:06,100 --> 00:24:06,700
Yes.

504
00:24:10,220 --> 00:24:10,860
Mother,

505
00:24:11,740 --> 00:24:12,740
come with me to the palace.

506
00:24:18,300 --> 00:24:19,420
As you wish.

507
00:24:22,920 --> 00:24:25,190
[Hanqiu Palace]

508
00:24:42,180 --> 00:24:43,100
Did you manage

509
00:24:43,860 --> 00:24:44,980
to remember what was said earlier?

510
00:24:49,380 --> 00:24:52,500
Give me those bloodstained clothes.

511
00:24:52,820 --> 00:24:54,100
I'll clean them for you.

512
00:24:54,980 --> 00:24:56,340
Over the years,

513
00:24:56,860 --> 00:24:58,900
I haven't really taken good care of you.

514
00:24:59,740 --> 00:25:02,660
I'll get you a few new outfits later.

515
00:25:02,940 --> 00:25:04,260
When you're facing Her Highness,

516
00:25:04,460 --> 00:25:06,540
you should pay more attention
to your appearance and manners.

517
00:25:07,380 --> 00:25:07,980
Okay.

518
00:25:16,540 --> 00:25:18,700
That umbrella and his outfit

519
00:25:19,300 --> 00:25:21,180
are exactly the same
as they were in the past.

520
00:25:22,060 --> 00:25:25,180
♪May time itself ask me♪

521
00:25:25,180 --> 00:25:27,940
♪How many glances does it take
in a lifetime♪

522
00:25:27,940 --> 00:25:32,660
♪To be blessed
with your highs and your lows?♪

523
00:25:33,780 --> 00:25:35,540
♪I've cherished every second of my life♪

524
00:25:35,540 --> 00:25:39,580
♪Embracing your joys and sorrows♪

525
00:25:39,580 --> 00:25:41,020
♪Serenely♪

526
00:25:41,020 --> 00:25:44,660
♪Allowing the flower of love to bloom♪

527
00:25:45,060 --> 00:25:45,740
Rongqing.

528
00:25:45,820 --> 00:25:48,580
♪I thought capturing your heart
meant forever♪

529
00:25:48,580 --> 00:25:50,620
♪Yet, it turned out to be
as fleeting as autumn♪

530
00:25:50,620 --> 00:25:52,780
♪Without you♪

531
00:25:52,900 --> 00:25:56,100
♪Even the hustle and bustle
can still feel lonely♪

532
00:25:57,460 --> 00:26:02,820
♪I'd follow you with no hesitation♪

533
00:26:03,140 --> 00:26:07,420
♪Ready to surrender everything
to this sensation♪

534
00:26:08,500 --> 00:26:12,740
♪Even if past moments
vanish without a trace♪

535
00:26:12,740 --> 00:26:13,740
Bring my mother there.

536
00:26:14,060 --> 00:26:15,100
I need to go over there now.

537
00:26:15,100 --> 00:26:16,980
♪Grant me a ceaseless passion♪

538
00:26:16,980 --> 00:26:17,660
Wenxuan.

539
00:26:17,860 --> 00:26:19,260
Where are you going, Wenxuan?

540
