Wenxuan is the Prince Consort

826
00:42:01,860 --> 00:42:03,020
and has returned.

827
00:42:03,140 --> 00:42:04,500
It was so humiliating for me

828
00:42:04,540 --> 00:42:07,100
to ask you for money,

829
00:42:07,100 --> 00:42:08,460
and yet you refuse to repay me.

830
00:42:09,420 --> 00:42:10,980
How can you be so shameless?

831
00:42:11,140 --> 00:42:11,860
You...

832
00:42:12,100 --> 00:42:13,580
Second Uncle.

833
00:42:14,220 --> 00:42:15,260
My mother's intention

