843
00:42:37,420 --> 00:42:39,100
It's not like that.

844
00:42:39,100 --> 00:42:39,620
Please let me explain.

845
00:42:39,620 --> 00:42:40,780
I don't want to hear your explanation.

846
00:42:40,780 --> 00:42:41,900
I already know everything.

847
00:42:41,980 --> 00:42:43,020
What do you know?

848
00:42:43,020 --> 00:42:45,620
