I'm simply taking care of it
on his behalf.

872
00:43:25,180 --> 00:43:25,860
A bit much?

873
00:43:26,380 --> 00:43:27,260
But you've done well.

874
00:43:30,100 --> 00:43:31,100
Pei Wenxuan

875
00:43:31,220 --> 00:43:33,020
